# Logo Design

## Name
Hayat Tofik

## Track
Graphic Design Internship

## Description
This project was created as part of the Oasis Infobyte Graphic Design Internship Program.

The objective of this task was to create an original and minimalist logo that represents a brand identity. The logo was designed in different variations, including a full-color version, a monochrome version, and a white version on a dark background.

